  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2></strong><br>Gedaria is a <strong>2D adventure puzzle-platformer</strong>, from a Czech independent game developer team of two high school students. The game takes place in the past. You will take on a role of a peasant Vladimir, on the way to the liberation of his kidnapped family… The game will surely captivate you with its simple but beautiful autumn atmosphere and<strong> non-traditional game mechanics.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/f00177a3474b11424597438a72b3e031.poster.avif?t=1671292802\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/f00177a3474b11424597438a72b3e031.webm?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/f00177a3474b11424597438a72b3e031.mp4?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Character</h2></strong><br>The main character Vladimir is the son of a farmer, an ordinary boy who finds a <strong>legendary rake</strong>, which gives him the ability to rake leaves into piles and solve puzzles across levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/d7e42927da38bef2a3e0a9c3b740f057.poster.avif?t=1671292802\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/d7e42927da38bef2a3e0a9c3b740f057.webm?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/d7e42927da38bef2a3e0a9c3b740f057.mp4?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Mechanics</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Piles of leaves,<br></li><li>leaf holders,<br></li><li>wind,<br></li><li>quick-leaves (quick sand made of leaves 😉),<br></li><li>leaves,<br></li><li>leaf blower.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/c7c31dc82d843f310d16ef1174a6ceac.poster.avif?t=1671292802\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/c7c31dc82d843f310d16ef1174a6ceac.webm?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/c7c31dc82d843f310d16ef1174a6ceac.mp4?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2></strong><br>Gedaria is a <strong>2D adventure puzzle-platformer</strong>, from a Czech independent game developer team of two high school students. The game takes place in the past. You will take on a role of a peasant Vladimir, on the way to the liberation of his kidnapped family… The game will surely captivate you with its simple but beautiful autumn atmosphere and<strong> non-traditional game mechanics.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/f00177a3474b11424597438a72b3e031.poster.avif?t=1671292802\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/f00177a3474b11424597438a72b3e031.webm?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/f00177a3474b11424597438a72b3e031.mp4?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Character</h2></strong><br>The main character Vladimir is the son of a farmer, an ordinary boy who finds a <strong>legendary rake</strong>, which gives him the ability to rake leaves into piles and solve puzzles across levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/d7e42927da38bef2a3e0a9c3b740f057.poster.avif?t=1671292802\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/d7e42927da38bef2a3e0a9c3b740f057.webm?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/d7e42927da38bef2a3e0a9c3b740f057.mp4?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Mechanics</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Piles of leaves,<br></li><li>leaf holders,<br></li><li>wind,<br></li><li>quick-leaves (quick sand made of leaves 😉),<br></li><li>leaves,<br></li><li>leaf blower.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/c7c31dc82d843f310d16ef1174a6ceac.poster.avif?t=1671292802\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/c7c31dc82d843f310d16ef1174a6ceac.webm?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679880/extras/c7c31dc82d843f310d16ef1174a6ceac.mp4?t=1671292802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
